short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Expand and Filter Github Messages, to make team commits and comments easier to read

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Open source project, to help filter Githhub Pull Request messages.

A button is added to git that, when activated, hides the Github Actions and thus facilitates the reading of the team's commits and comments.

The extension does not collect any information from you, to keep your security.

https://github.com/williamarcondes/github-filter-messages
